{"tid":1981382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國股市數據異常！聯結ETF價格大亂","createTime":"2020-04-20T15:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T17:56:30.000Z","uid":75656,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"089af594ea074ba52c1e80cae013dc4c331f49e4","tid":1981382,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:38:33.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕多家中國媒體報導，週一（20日）早盤，中國股市包括滬深300指數、中證1000指數等部份跨市場指數數據出現異常，漲跌幅與追蹤的指數基金不符，對此上海證券交易所也在上午發出公告，表示正會同相關公司調查原因。<br />\n<br />\n《新浪財經》報導，今（20日）早盤滬深300指數下跌2.6%，中證1000指數漲幅則超過6%，創業成長指數下跌24%；不過在相關ETF方面，華太柏瑞300ETF盤中漲跌幅最多不超過0.3%，南方中證1000ETF漲幅則不到1%。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，基金業人士指出，正在和交易所還有指數公司聯絡；對此上海證券交易所也在官網發出公告，正會同指數編制的機構中證指數公司，針對相關原因進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n根據Wind彙整的數據顯示，追蹤滬深300指數的基金，包括ETF及其聯結基金等，以及場外指數基金，約超過200檔，規模則超過千億人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3139267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3139267&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzWg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=3d31eeb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3139267&h=ed935c03\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3139267</a>"},{"pid":"beae64ac3b61c7d8462a421119a1b69281363fb0","tid":1981382,"uid":134415,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"印錢都費事 直接改點數"},{"pid":"3f3b7574f0e81cb157c0c003dd15bf35ea50af89","tid":1981382,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:41:11.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒<br />\n領導先走"},{"pid":"6dd842646a4b7ab934e072844510e05ec7ece86f","tid":1981382,"uid":134744,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"開始頂唔順<br />\n要做假了"},{"pid":"f52efae8fbb5cff799059598ddc601c1cd63bfe3","tid":1981382,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pHifgst.png\" data-thum